&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a qualified Nursing Associate or Assistant Practitioner to work in our busy and friendly Nursing Team currently based at the Withywood Centre.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be experienced with face to face nursing care and required to work with a wide range of service users across South Bristol to perform holistic assessments and deliver essential nursing tasks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Though community experience would be desirable we will support you to gain the skills that you will need to perform your role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note: this role is for qualified practitioners only.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information on this exiting role please contact Anna Dash or Ellie Gould on 07920210814 or 07900264417&lt;/p&gt;
